# All text stays LF everywhere. The embedded payload (cli/src/generated/
# sotPayload.ts) stores LF bytes and `generate-sot-payload.ts --check`
# compares the SoT/ checkout against it byte-for-byte — a CRLF checkout
# (core.autocrlf=true on Windows runners) makes every text file "stale".
* text=auto eol=lf

# Shell entrypoints must stay LF — a CRLF checkout breaks Git Bash with
# `/bin/bash^M` before any logic runs.
docks-kit text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
